Two suspected thugs were last nightshot dead along Jogoo Road, Nairobi.Two pistols were also recovered.Police are looking for their accomplice who escaped on a motorbike.The suspects, according to police have been behind a series of robberies in the area.In the last three days, a total of 12 thugs have been shot dead in Nairobi.On Wednesday, police shot and killed three suspected thugs in a botched robbery in Parklands area.The gang was driving away on First Avenue near Avenue Hospital, in a Voxy van they had stolen.Police found a pistol with eight bullets and ID cards.They said the suspects were on a mission to commit another robbery.Read: [PHOTOS] Three shot dead in botched Parklands robbery